---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="SEO Optimization Services | MarketOps" description="Rank your website higher on Google with proven SEO strategies. We handle On-page, Off-page, Local, Technical, and E-commerce SEO to scale organic conversions.">
  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="hero-wrapper">
    <div class="hero-overlay" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(11, 15, 25, 0.4) 0%, var(--bg-main) 100%);"></div>
    <div class="container" style="position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center;">
      <div class="reveal-on-scroll">
        <div class="badge-lead">Search Engine Optimization</div>
        <h1 class="gradient-text" style="font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 4.2rem); max-width: 950px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;">
          Rank Your Website Higher on Google with <br><span class="gradient-text-alt" style="font-weight: 800;">Proven SEO Strategies</span>
        </h1>
        <p style="font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.25rem); color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;">
          Stop paying for every single click. Build long-term authority, organic traffic channels, and reliable search ranks that drive sales while you sleep.
        </p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a href="#calendly" class="btn btn-primary">Get Free SEO Audit</a>
          <a href="#challenges" class="btn btn-secondary">See SEO Challenges</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CHALLENGES SECTION -->
  <section id="challenges" class="section-padding" style="background: #0d121f;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal-on-scroll" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 5rem;">
        <div class="badge-lead">Common Challenges</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Common Challenges Before SEO in Today’s Digital Era</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto;">Organic search landscape is highly competitive. Without smart SEO, your website gets buried under competitors.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">📉</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Low Organic Reach</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Websites struggle to get traffic without proper optimization strategies. You might have a great design, but search engines simply cannot discover your pages.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">💸</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Increasing Ad Costs</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Paid advertising is expensive and rates rise every quarter, making organic SEO an absolute necessity to maintain high overall business margins and healthy ROI.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">⚡</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Slow Website Speed</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Slow loading speed, poor mobile experience, and bad technical structures directly ruin search visibility rankings and push buyers to click away.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🛡️</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Poor User Experience</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Missing standard search engine optimization configurations leads to poor structure, broken navigation flows, and technical security indexing issues.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOLUTIONS SECTION -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background: var(--bg-main);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal-on-scroll" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 5rem;">
        <div class="badge-lead">Our Method</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">How We Fix It — Our SEO Method</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">We use data-driven, white-hat frameworks to permanently claim rankings on search engines.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-5" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll" style="padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
          <div style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">01</div>
          <h4 style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600;">Audit</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.4;">
            Deep technical crawling to find indexing errors.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll" style="padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
          <div style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">02</div>
          <h4 style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600;">Keyword</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.4;">
            Finding high-intent terms for maximum conversion.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll" style="padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
          <div style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">03</div>
          <h4 style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600;">Optimize</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.4;">
            On-page changes, meta tuning, and content structure.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll" style="padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
          <div style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">04</div>
          <h4 style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600;">Link Building</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.4;">
            High authority backlinks to build global trust signals.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 5 -->
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll" style="padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
          <div style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">05</div>
          <h4 style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600;">Reporting</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.4;">
            Transparent KPI reporting and rank adjustments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE VERTICALS SECTION -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background: #080c14; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal-on-scroll" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 5rem;">
        <div class="badge-lead">SEO Verticals</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Our Comprehensive SEO Services</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">Dedicated search strategies engineered for every business model.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">✍️</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">On-Page SEO</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Improves rankings, increases organic traffic, enhances user experience, and helps search engines understand and index your website content effectively.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🌐</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Off-Page SEO</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Builds website authority through backlinks, brand mentions, and external signals, improving rankings, trust, credibility, and organic traffic from search engines.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">📍</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Local SEO</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Helps your business appear in nearby searches, improves Google Maps visibility, attracts local customers, and increases calls, visits, and sales.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">⚙️</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Technical SEO</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Improves website speed, crawlability, indexing, mobile performance, and security, helping search engines understand your site and boost rankings effectively.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🛍️</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">E-Commerce SEO</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Improves product visibility, boosts organic traffic, enhances rankings, and increases online sales by optimizing product pages, categories, and shopping experience.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">📈</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Landing Page Optimization</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Increases conversions, improves user experience, and reduces bounce rate for better leads and sales.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQS SECTION -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background: #080c14; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal-on-scroll" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
        <div class="badge-lead">FAQ</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">Everything you need to know about our SEO and Rank Optimization solutions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-wrapper reveal-on-scroll">
        <!-- Item 1 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">1. What is SEO and how does it work?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>SEO (Search Engine Optimization) improves your website's organic visibility on search engines like Google by optimizing content relevance, keywords, and technical structure.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 2 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">2. How long does SEO take to show results?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>SEO typically takes 3–6 months to establish initial authority and rankings depending on search competition, website condition, and niche keywords strategy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 3 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">3. Do you provide Local SEO services?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>Yes, Local SEO services help your business rank at the top of nearby localized searches and Google Maps business listings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 4 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">4. Is SEO better than paid ads?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>SEO gives compound, long-term organic results and high authority without recurring spend per click, while paid ads provide instant but temporary traffic.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 5 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">5. Will SEO increase my sales?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>Yes, by targeting users who are actively searching for your products or services, SEO drives highly qualified, high-intent traffic to improve conversions and sales growth.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 6 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">6. What is E-commerce SEO?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>E-commerce SEO optimizes product listing pages, parent category links, brand collections, and overall store navigation patterns to boost organic transactions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 7 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">7. How do you measure SEO success?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>We measure results using Google Search Console and analytics to track organic keyword impressions, search visibility, rankings, and conversions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 8 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">8. Do you fix SEO issues on existing websites?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>Yes, we perform extensive audits and fix technical layout, on-page content, slow speed loads, and indexing issues on legacy setups.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 9 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">9. Is SEO a one-time process?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>No, SEO is an ongoing maintenance and growth process. Competitors, search algorithms, and consumer behavior shift continuously, necessitating regular optimization.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 10 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">10. What is a Google ranking factor?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>Google ranks sites based on over 200 signals, primarily content relevance and depth, backlink authority, page speed, mobile adaptability, and core web vitals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CALENDLY EMBED SECTION -->
  <section id="calendly" class="section-padding" style="background: var(--bg-main);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal-on-scroll" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Setup Your Free Organic SEO Audit</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">Connect with an organic ranking specialist today to analyze search visibility gaps and technical glitches.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="calendly-section reveal-on-scroll">
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; padding: 2rem;">
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What We Will Discover:</h3>
            <ul style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start;">
                <span style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan); font-weight: bold;">[01]</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.15rem;">Organic Keyword Indexing Gaps</h4>
                  <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem;">Find the high-intent keywords driving leads to your top competitors that you rank poorly for.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start;">
                <span style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan); font-weight: bold;">[02]</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.15rem;">Core Technical SEO Checklist</h4>
                  <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem;">Identify crawl budget drains, missing schemas, broken URLs, and site performance blockers.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start;">
                <span style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan); font-weight: bold;">[03]</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.15rem;">Authority Scaling Strategy</h4>
                  <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem;">A solid off-page backlink roadmap to increase your domain authority score organically.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2.5rem; text-align: center;">
            <h4 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--font-heading);">Schedule Session</h4>
            <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Select slot on our live team calendar</p>
            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;">
              <a href="https://wa.me/919424995426" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">💬 WhatsApp Direct booking</a>
              <a href="mailto:connect@marketops.in" class="btn btn-secondary" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">📧 Email: connect@marketops.in</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
